Weimar stands united once again! Our worker support is somewhat shaken due to cooperation with the center-right, whilst our reputation amongst the new middle class is better than ever. Support for the republic has greatly increased, and so do our relations with our renewed partners. The left is in uproar.

@no_agreement
subtitle: The workers will applaud us for not caving in to the burgeouisie!
